 SSD 了）。", "last_modified": 1623402673, "replies": 29, "id": 782959}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1607656854", "name": "macos", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1607656854", "title": "macOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos", "topics": 16708, "footer": "<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1607656854", "stars": 4318, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "xuegy", "website": "", "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a14fd036007f13550119309d4ee7e0f1?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xuegy", "tagline": "", "twitter": null, "created": 1421601097, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a14fd036007f13550119309d4ee7e0f1?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a14fd036007f13550119309d4ee7e0f1?s=24&d=retro", "location": "", "btc": null, "id": 92500}, "last_reply_by": "cwbsw", "last_touched": 1623440338, "title": "双路 E5 在 M1 面前很尴尬", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/783020", "created": 1623425292, "content": "双路 E5-2667v2 （ 16 核 3.3GHz，睿频 4.0GHz ），128GB ECC 内存，AMD W5100 亮机卡\r\n\r\n虽然已经知道 M1 吊打顶配垃圾桶的事实，但还是对双路系统抱有幻想，直到我跑了个 Geekbench：\r\n\r\n单核 855\r\n\r\n多核 9949\r\n\r\nMetal 15865\r\n\r\n对比新买的 M1 Mac mini 16GB：\r\n\r\n单核 1749\r\n\r\n多核 7682\r\n\r\nMetal 22940\r\n\r\n事实证明这套洋垃圾在 10 倍功耗的前提下，多核性能优势只有 30%，唯一的优点就剩下大内存了。", "content_rendered": "<p>双路 E5-2667v2 （ 16 核 3.3GHz，睿频 4.0GHz ），128GB ECC 内存，AMD W5100 亮机卡</p>\n<p>虽然已经知道 M1 吊打顶配垃圾桶的事实，但还是对双路系统抱有幻想，直到我跑了个 Geekbench：</p>\n<p>单核 855</p>\n<p>多核 9949</p>\n<p>Metal 15865</p>\n<p>对比新买的 M1 Mac mini 16GB：</p>\n<p>单核 1749</p>\n<p>多核 7682</p>\n<p>Metal 22940</p>\n<p>事实证明这套洋垃圾在 10 倍功耗的前提下，多核性能优势只有 30%，唯一的优点就剩下大内存了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1623425292, "replies": 26, "id": 783020}]